=======================
 One Fighting Game ...
=======================

----------------------
 ... To Rule Them All
----------------------


Plot
====

One button, one hit, one winner.


Gameplay
========

One button:

- when standing -> jump
- when jumping -> kick
- when kicking -> guard (have to be frame perfect)

There's no recovery.


